# =====================================================================
# Frontend environment variables
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local`) and adjust as needed.
# All variables MUST start with VITE_ to be exposed to the client code.
# After changing values you need to restart `npm run dev`.
# =====================================================================

# Base URL the frontend uses for all API requests.
#
# Local development (default — leave commented):
#   The Vite dev server proxies `/api` to http://localhost:5000
#   (configured in vite.config.js), so you don't need to set this.
#
# Production / staging:
#   Set this to the full URL of your deployed backend, e.g.
#   VITE_API_BASE=https://api.alarish-tarvels.com/api
#
# VITE_API_BASE=/api
